         Asm:  Its pretty rare that we're unable to land anything on a mob given our breath of spell lines.  In the Velk example, our fire based spells land just fine as does poison.  Velk is immune to magic and dis (and cold i assume).</P><P>As far as kunark goes, the resists on most of these mobs is rediculous.  Take trak for example.  I'm unable to land anything on him, this is including GToZ.  My value on a trak raid is single pulling him, buffing everyone with DMF and then landing a lifeburn to help contribute to the kill.  I agree with bril, VI should look at the resist checks on these mobs and maybe up the HP's a bit to compensate for it.  A 100k hp trak would be a fun encounter, assuming he wasnt resistant to everything.</P><P>As for lures, as they stand right now on live servers, lures are low resist spells, not unresistable.  Banes are unresistable spells (aka the giant and dragon bane wizzie spells).  Most wizzies i know rarely use their lure lines, as its uncommon for a mob to be immune to magic, fire and cold based attacks in addition to the poor mana efficiency of the lures themselves.  Wizzies will simply shift their dd line appropriately, given the resists of a mob.</P><P>I do agree though, when a mob is immune to magic and fire, its just too limiting too our class as far as our dmg capacity.  I have yet to land a CoC on a boss mob, EB and plague have such high resist rates and the agro on all 3 dot lines as we all know - only beg's a summons.  I think the best solution to the problem is providing us with 2 new Cold Based Dots.  One around 51ish and another around 59 or 60.  These dots shouldnt be as mana effiicient as our fire line, but still have the near lure resist checks.  Given a cold line of dots, it should be rare that we are unable to effectively dmg a mob via dot stacking.  Only a small handful of mobs in EQ are immune to fire, magic and cold based attacks. Tunare and trak are the only 2 i can think of atm.</P><P>Tencor Laureate - 60th Warlock<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=55675" target="_blank">My Profile</a><BR><a href="http://www.veilofsilence.org" target="_blank">Veil of Silence</a> <BR>Innoruuk Server<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
